                        <interp inst="t18670128-name-39" type="surname" value="PETTY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18670128-name-39" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE PETTY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman</hi> 96 <hi rend="italic">K</hi>). On the 3rd of January I was called, and took the prisoner—this shilling was on the counter—he said, "I tried to pass that shilling, but on Saturday I was not in the neighbourhood; I did not try to pass the half-crown"—I only found a penny on him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
